## Expected outcome

All five engineering base personas (`docs/AE/personas/_base/`), the two target-applied AEH roles (`docs/AE/roles/`), and the check script (`docs/AE/bin/aeh-practice-check.sh`, executable) are byte-identical with harness master. Subsequent role-bound prompts and `health` passes in this target session load the latest behaviour.

## Fallback

- If any snapshot directory is missing: halt and surface (step 1); create it before copying.
- If any file copy fails: halt at the failed artifact, surface details, leave subsequent artifacts untouched. Operator addresses the failure, then re-runs the retrofit which is idempotent.
- If `cmp` reports mismatch immediately after copy: halt with file-content diff; this indicates a copy error (rare) or an active write conflict.
